---
title: Quick Rustic Herby Bacon & Leek Fusilli with Garden Salad & Double Parmesan Cheese
description: Twirly-whirly pasta mixed through a creamy sauce is too good to be true. There’s plenty of veggies hidden in amongst the fusilli to keep things fresh and green. For a bit of fun, throw in some diced bacon and leek and you’ve cooked another pasta winner dinner.

